data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the Hearth Stone neighborhood! This property is situated right next to Pinnacle Hills Uptown, The AMP, Top Golf, the Promenade, and many restaurants and shops, offering a wealth of entertainment and convenience. This inviting and open floor plan seamlessly connects the living spaces, creating the perfect setting for both entertaining and enjoying time with your family. With 5 bedrooms, including a versatile 5th bedroom upstairs that can serve as a bonus room or guest suite, there's space for everyone with endless possibilities. Relax on the back screened-in porch or by the outdoor fire pit, and enjoy the unique benefit of having no neighbors behind the house! Amenities include a community pool, playground, club house, and an outdoor basketball court. Zoned for Bentonville Schools. Sellers are providing a 1-Year Home Warranty with the home, and Refrigerator and Washer & Dryer stay! Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours in one of the best locations in NWA!
